            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
              <li><strong>System Thinkers</strong> who see the big picture</li>
              <li><strong>Data Architects</strong> who build information highways</li>
              <li><strong>AI Innovators</strong> who teach machines to understand railways</li>
              <li><strong>Problem Solvers</strong> who turn complexity into clarity</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
              Our 15-person team operates at the bleeding edge of machine intelligence,
              enterprise software design, and large-scale data analytics. Every project
              we touch becomes a testament to what's possible when brilliant minds
              collaborate with purpose.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Mission Card -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500/10 to-purple-500/10 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-blue-500/20">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">üéØ Our Mission</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            To redefine railway management through AI, data, and software excellence,
            creating digital infrastructures that are smarter, faster, and more 
            sustainable than ever imagined.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Vision Card -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500/10 to-blue-500/10 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-cyan-500/20 mb-16">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">üöÄ Our Vision</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300">
          To become a global benchmark for AI-powered industrial software solutions,
          setting the standards for digital transformation in rail, transport, and
          beyond‚Äîinspiring an entire generation of infrastructure technology.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Our Culture -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-purple-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
          How We Work
        </h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-dark-tertiary/50 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/10">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Collaborative Excellence</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm mb-4">
              We thrive in an agile, cross-functional environment where every voice 
              matters. From junior engineers to senior architects, everyone contributes
              to architectural decisions, code reviews, and innovation sprints.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-gray-400 text-sm space-y-1">
              <li>‚Ä¢ Daily standups with purpose</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Bi-weekly innovation labs</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Quarterly hackathons</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Continuous learning budget</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-dark-tertiary/50 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/10">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Startup Energy, Enterprise Discipline</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm mb-4">
              We combine the creativity and speed of a startup with the rigor and 
              reliability of enterprise engineering. This unique blend allows us to
              experiment boldly while delivering mission-critical systems.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-gray-400 text-sm space-y-1">
              <li>‚Ä¢ Rapid prototyping cycles</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Production-grade quality gates</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ 20% time for R&D</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Fail fast, learn faster</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-dark-tertiary/50 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/10">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Human-Centered Technology</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm mb-4">
              Technology serves people, not the other way around. Every system we 
              build prioritizes user experience, operator safety, and societal impact.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-gray-400 text-sm space-y-1">
              <li>‚Ä¢ User research integration</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Accessibility-first design</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Safety-critical standards</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Social responsibility</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- The Journey Timeline -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-purple-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
          From Vision to Reality
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="bg-dark-tertiary/50 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/10 border-l-4 border-l-blue-500">
            <div class="text-blue-400 font-bold mb-2">2019 - The Genesis</div>
            <p class="text-gray-300">
              Born from a vision within PiA Group's innovation lab. A small team
              of 5 passionate engineers asked: "What if we could make railways 
              as intelligent as modern AI?" This question sparked a movement.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-dark-tertiary/50 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/10 border-l-4 border-l-purple-500">
            <div class="text-purple-400 font-bold mb-2">2020 - First Breakthrough</div>
            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-2">
              Delivered Turkey's first national-scale microservices architecture
              for railway management. The DDYS project became a case study in 
              digital transformation, catching the attention of transport authorities
              across the region.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Achievement: 500+ microservices, 99.9% uptime</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-dark-tertiary/50 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/10 border-l-4 border-l-cyan-500">
            <div class="text-cyan-400 font-bold mb-2">2021 - Scaling Innovation</div>
            <p class="text-gray-300">
              Team doubled to 10 engineers. Expanded our tech stack to include
              advanced AI/ML frameworks. Launched our first predictive maintenance
              models, reducing equipment failure rates by 40%.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-dark-tertiary/50 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/10 border-l-4 border-l-green-500">
            <div class="text-green-400 font-bold mb-2">2022 - AI Integration Era</div>
            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-2">
              Pivoted hard into AI-driven analytics and agent-based automation.
              Introduced Large Language Models for natural language querying of
              railway data. Built our first autonomous decision-making agents.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Innovation: Real-time anomaly detection using deep learning</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-dark-tertiary/50 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/10 border-l-4 border-l-blue-500">
            <div class="text-blue-400 font-bold mb-2">2023 - Platform Maturity</div>
            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-2">
              The Big Data Analytics Platform goes live. Unified data from 50+
              sources into a single intelligence hub. Kubernetes orchestration
              at scale. GIS integration for live asset tracking.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Impact: 10TB+ data processed daily</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-dark-tertiary/50 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/10 border-l-4 border-l-purple-500">
            <div class="text-purple-400 font-bold mb-2">2024 - Recognition & Growth</div>
            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-2">
              Recognized as TCDD's trusted digital transformation partner. Team
              reaches 15 elite engineers. Began research into next-generation
              AI agents and Model Context Protocol (MCP) integration.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Status: Industry leader in railway AI solutions</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-dark-tertiary/50 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/10 border-l-4 border-l-cyan-500">
            <div class="text-cyan-400 font-bold mb-2">2025 & Beyond - The Future</div>
            <p class="text-gray-300">
              Expanding into autonomous railway operations, edge AI deployment,
              and cross-border interoperability platforms. Our vision: make every
              railway on Earth intelligent, connected, and sustainable.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Team Philosophy -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500/10 via-purple-500/10 to-cyan-500/10 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/10 text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">The RailDevHub Way</h2>
        <blockquote class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 via-purple-500 to-cyan-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-6">
          "Every project is more than a product‚Äîit's a story of collaboration,
          precision engineering, and human-centered innovation. We don't just
          write code; we architect the future."
        </blockquote>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mt-8">
          <div class="text-gray-300">üé® Creativity meets structure</div>
          <div class="text-gray-300">üî¨ Research-driven development</div>
          <div class="text-gray-300">ü§ù Radical collaboration</div>
          <div class="text-gray-300">üìö Continuous learning culture</div>
          <div class="text-gray-300">üåü Excellence is standard, not exception</div>
          <div class="text-gray-300">üöÄ Ship fast, iterate faster</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>

